Context("Numeric");

#given
$lh = random(10,20,1);
$rh = random(45,70,1);
$rp = random(120,160,1);

#computation 
$lp = $rp/$rh*$lh;

#set tolerance
Context()->flags->set(
tolerance=>.01);

##############################################################
#
#  Text 
#
#

BEGIN_PGML

A golfer's hands move through an arc length of [`[$lh]`] [`cm`] during a putt. What arc length does the head of the putter move through if the hands are [`[$rh]`] [`cm`] from the axis of rotation and the putter's head is [`[$rp]`] [`cm`] from the axis of rotation?

[`l=`] [_____]{"$lp"} [`cm`]  

END_PGML

